    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the world of <i>Homeward</i>!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a rookie police officer, you’re tasked with much more than law enforcement. In this heartwarming 2D pixel art adventure, you’ll complete missions, solve mysteries, and help your neighbor, Jenny, find her missing cat, Mac. Explore a charming, open world full of engaging quests, delightful mini-games, and meaningful career choices that lead to multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔍 Explore a Vibrant Open World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roam through bustling neighborhoods, peaceful parks, and lively locales as you interact with quirky characters and uncover hidden secrets. Every corner holds a new adventure! Take a break from missions, explore the map, or simply relax—there’s always something to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/e2f64ee6d03b381350734a601ab5059a.poster.avif?t=1729640923\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/e2f64ee6d03b381350734a601ab5059a.webm?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/e2f64ee6d03b381350734a601ab5059a.mp4?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🕵️‍♂️ Complete Engaging Missions</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on diverse missions that test your detective skills. From solving petty crimes to helping locals with their everyday troubles, every choice matters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/9b2eeff32fdebe61fb753bda70587664.poster.avif?t=1729640923\" width=800 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/9b2eeff32fdebe61fb753bda70587664.webm?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/9b2eeff32fdebe61fb753bda70587664.mp4?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧩 Solve Mysteries with Mini-Games</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to the test with fun mini-games that add variety to your detective work. These games help you gather clues, unlock new areas, and climb the police ranks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌈 Nostalgic Pixel Art &amp; Sound Design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get lost in a beautifully crafted pixel art world, filled with warmth and charm. The soothing soundtrack brings the town to life, creating a heartwarming atmosphere throughout your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🐈‍ A Story with Heart (and Cats!)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based loosely on a true story, <i>Homeward</i> is filled with characters inspired by real-life cats. Choose to play as either Amelia or George and dive into a world where every name holds a special meaning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/d8c72ef9b2b257c023b5ac6068b105ad.poster.avif?t=1729640923\" width=140 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/d8c72ef9b2b257c023b5ac6068b105ad.webm?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/d8c72ef9b2b257c023b5ac6068b105ad.mp4?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/8bc451ef46150cee274264bfd2c3f647.poster.avif?t=1729640923\" width=140 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/8bc451ef46150cee274264bfd2c3f647.webm?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289500/extras/8bc451ef46150cee274264bfd2c3f647.mp4?t=1729640923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌐 Learn More</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peek behind the scenes and discover more about <i>Homeward</i> at our website.</p>",
